# Exclude test fixtures and goldens from the published archive.
# The golden outputs under test/golden/outputs/ are expected-output snapshots
# of generator runs and intentionally import flutter / flutter_solidart, which
# are not declared as deps of solid_generator (they belong to consumer apps).
# Shipping them would trigger pub.dev import-validation warnings without
# adding any value for downstream users — they don't run the generator's tests.
test/
